00:00:05.580 --> 00:00:07.980
So why can't some people give blood?

00:00:07.980 --> 00:00:12.720
Is this science, or prejudice?

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:17.380
Hello humans, Trace here for DNews.

00:00:17.380 --> 00:00:19.990
Blood donation is seen by some, as a civil
right.

00:00:19.990 --> 00:00:23.970
People making a sacrifice, literally weakening
themselves, to help strangers.

00:00:23.970 --> 00:00:29.119
But, according to the FDA, men who have sex
with men -- known as MSM -- aren't treated

00:00:29.119 --> 00:00:33.930
equally when it comes to blood donation, and
some have gone as far to imply they're banned

00:00:33.930 --> 00:00:35.059
from doing so.

00:00:35.059 --> 00:00:36.319
Firstly, that's not true.

00:00:36.319 --> 00:00:40.079
Men who have sex with men, (as well as women
and transgender persons who have sex with

00:00:40.079 --> 00:00:46.409
